            . I saw the prisoner on the 26th of April take a pair of half-boots from a chair or stool at the door of Mr. Simmons, in Saffron-hill - I knocked at the door, and asked if they had not lost a pair of half-boots; I then followed the prisoner, and the Police-man took him with them.</p>
